{"tid":1467951,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"輸你老味咩輸","createTime":"2019-08-13T17:45:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T18:12:26.000Z","uid":81789,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"ce7784e065b58493b5523d43632b8e9625ec8d05","tid":1467951,"uid":81789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:45:39.000Z","msg":"失敗主義做乜啫<br />\n做得唔完美咪改<br />\n之前紅隧話塞都變到免費放行<br />\n癱離境都一樣可以變到<br />\n有巴打話放一條長龍比佢地慢慢排<br />\n是但一個解決方案提供到比旅客咪咩都易傾<br />\n捉鬼又係 你打死佢最多咪少左啲鬼<br />\n你捉到影完相拎好彈藥咪送佢開心離開<br />\n有哂樣有哂相你日後搵佢私了撚有人知咩<br />\n都係果句 <br />\n核爆都唔割蓆 <br />\n有咩咪大家兄弟一齊硬食"},{"pid":"8df0513eb04f52a4b59a163a413346a4ebeaa478","tid":1467951,"uid":229840,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:46:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不分化，不割席！<br />\n核彈都唔割！！！！</span></span>"},{"pid":"56fd82749460f37a6c7ee85a75d8d905cf3b59bf","tid":1467951,"uid":109820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:47:40.000Z","msg":"不割！！！<br />\n<br />\n【跪求大家入黎睇下，我好想香港贏】關於鬼關於衝動<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1466732\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1466732</a>"},{"pid":"ba663ea434161dac8dc81443f295931ea85a1cfe","tid":1467951,"uid":67232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:49:02.000Z","msg":"光復香港之前不如先光復連登<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1467151\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1467151</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a2f5236cf67d8ed2a9c0cf43925f293f0f90ce69","tid":1467951,"uid":42250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:49:10.000Z","msg":"黑 警 機 場 拔 槍 指 嚇 示 威 者 ！ 同 你 逐 格 睇 暨 聽 日 文 宣 方 向<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1467801\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1467801</a>"},{"pid":"18d818876e44440401a5adc2b1f13e3aaac008c1","tid":1467951,"uid":292067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:49:45.000Z","msg":"何妖實恥笑<br />\n我由頭到尾無割過 無被割 無被指責<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你地班撚樣 少少野都割又分化互屌互指責 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n---------<br />\n記住 反對/屌人時 比埋建議 咁就<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n幾句建議姐818 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />各自爬山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好多手足受傷 被捕 點解我地仲企出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因 為 未 完 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">818見</span>"},{"pid":"bb93aec4b88d50c41536adac1e9a66d6bcf90076","tid":1467951,"uid":66489,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:50:46.000Z","msg":"英雄所見！<br />\n核彈都唔割 要孭一齊孭！"},{"pid":"ff582fbfe026a6b1b0855e73f5458384eeb77aa4","tid":1467951,"uid":269433,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:57:57.000Z","msg":"對住呢個政府講良知係有用<br />\n我地唔需要流咁多血 犧牲咁多手足<br />\n打個公安叫輸? 手足比人拉就叫輸啦<br />\n核彈都唔割!<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">不分化 不割蓆<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n對準政權 各自爬山 </span></span>"},{"pid":"cd291d5b4f64b80119e87881bb70d1f224da0f3b","tid":1467951,"uid":81789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:07:35.000Z","msg":"團結"},{"pid":"abc55c67d28e095f8826a195dce54b482dde36b3","tid":1467951,"uid":180905,"like":0